metadata.name: WATCHER #2
metadata.description:
#[WATCHER ~Eyes of Legends~](https://play-nft.art/mints/watcher)

#【STORY】
The 『Eyes of Legends』collection, kept in a hidden warehouse by the Time Police, suddenly disappeared. As if in response to bloodline of Hades awakening for the first time in thousands of years The power of the pupil seems to have been restored. The power of heroes and villains who confronted Hades are sealed in the Eyes. To save the world or to misuse it, each with their own thoughts in mind. The battle for the 6666 pupils that hold the magic power begins.
